erlang-rocksdb 0.8.0 beta, released on 2017/05/17
=================================================

- replace custom pool by dirty-nif calls
- allows a cache to be shared between databases (option `block_cache``from the block options)
- allows an environment to be set and shared across databases (option `env`)
- add support of batch operations, allows to incrumentatly update a mutanle emory object
- addsupport for transaction log operations (riteration and replication)
